Sekuyiminyaka engama-30 selokhu u-Nelson Rolihlala Mandela akhululwa ejele i-Victor Verster, okungumzuzu emlandweni wethu ogqame kakhulu kuneminye inkululeko eke yaba nawo njengamanje.
Ngesikhathi eme kuvulandi ophezulu eHholo Ledolobha laseKapa ukuzokhuluma nezinkumbi zabantu ababefike ngezinkulungwane ngezinkulungwane ukuzomamukela, wathi:
'Indlela yethu eya enkululekweni ayijiki. Akumele sivumele ukusaba kume endleleni yethu.'
Njengamanje, emva kweminyaka engama-30, sisaqhubeka nokuya phambili ukwenza ngcono izimpilo zabantu bakithi, sisabhekana nezingqinamba, sisabekezelela izikhathi ezinzima, nathi-ke angeke sivumele ukusaba kume endleleni yethu.
Kumele siphokophele phambili, singavumeli ubunzima nokungabaza kusiphambukise.
Njengoba sihlangane ukuzobuka isimo sezwe lethu, sihlanganyele nomndeni ka-Basil February, iqhawe lenkululeko elinesibindi elashona eZimbabwe emkhankasweni i-Wankie ngonyaka we-1967.
Eminyakeni engama-50 indawo lapho elele khona, njengamanye amaqabane, kuze kube manje, ayaziwa.
Igalelo lakhe, ukuzinikelela kwakhe, akukaze kushaywe indiva.
Kusihlwa nje, sihlangene lapha sithotshwe izinkumbulo zalawo madoda nabafazi abanikelela ngezimpilo zabo enkululekweni yethu, sisazi kahle isibophezelo esikhulu esisiphethe sokufezekisa amaphupho abo.
Kulo nyaka, silungisa izisekelo.
Kunezikhathi la siphelelwa khona, kunezikhathi lapho senza amaphutha, kodwa siyaqhubeka nokungashukumiseki empokophelweni yethu yokwakha umphakathi okhululekile, olinganayo nonokuthula.
Umlando wethu usitshela ukuthi uma sibumbene ngokuthula nangokukholwa, singanqoba zonke izithiyo futhi siguqule izwe lethu libe indawo lapho sonke sizizwa sikhululekile, siphephile futhi sizizwe sintofontofo.
Kungaloyo moya njengamanje sizobhekana nesimo samanje.
Izwe lethu libhekene neqiniso elibabayo.
Umnotho wethu awukakhuli ngezinga elifanelekile eminyakeni engaphezu kweyishumi.
Noma imisebenzi yakhiwa, izinga lokungasebenzi liyaqhubeka nokukhuphuka.
Ukusimama komnotho wethu kumile ngenxa yokuthi ukushoda kwamandla ogesi okubelesele kuphazamisa amabhizinisi kanye nezimpilo zabantu.
Amabhizinisi amaningana kahulumeni asosizini, nezimali zikahulumeni wethu zingaphansi kwengcindezi enkulu.
Yinina, abantu baseNingizimu Afrika, enithwele lomthwalo, enibhekene nezindleko zokuphila ezikhuphukayo, ukungabikho kwemisebenzi, ukungakwazi ukubalekela inhlupheko, ukungakwazi ukubonisa okwazi ukukwenza.
Okwamanje, ngasikhathi sinye, kunenye ingxenye eqinisweni lethu.
Iqiniso lenani labantu abasha abafinyelela kalula kwezemfundo ukudlula phambilini futhi abathola imiphumela elokhu iba ngcono.
Iqiniso lezingane eziyisigidi ezi-2.4 ezisezindaweni zokukhulisa izingane ezincane nasezinkulisa.
Balinganiselwa kumaphesenti angama-81 abafundi abaphase umatikuletsheni ngonyaka odlule, nenani elandayo eliqhamuka ezikoleni zasemakhaya naselokishini.
Ngale mpumelelo enkulu, sishayela ihlombe Abafundi bangowezi-2019.
Iqiniso futhi ukuthi kunabafundi abayizi-720 000 abathole ukuxhaswa nguhulumeni ukufunda emakolishi amakhono nobuchwepheshe kanye nasemanyuvesi ngonyaka owedlule.
Sikhuluma ngabantu baseNingizimu Afrika abangaba yizigidi eziyi-6.8 abasaziyo isimo sabo seSandulelangculazi, bangaba izigidi ezi-5 abantu asebeqaliswe imishanguzo yokudambisa iSandulelangculazi kanye nabayizigidi ezi-4.2 abantu ngenxa yalokhu, ubungako begciwane egazini labo, abubonakali.
