Ekusebenzeni kwabantu abashu, ukusuka namuhla, siqala ukusebensiza uhlelo LukaMongameli Lokungenelela Ukusebenza Kwabantu Abasha - izinto eziyisithupha eziseqhulwini eminyakeni emihlanu ezayo ukunciphisa ukungasebenzi kwabantu abasha.
