INingizimu Afrika isibeke eqhulwini ukuthuthukiswa ngokwezomnotho kwabesifazane base-Afrika ngesikhathi sayo sokuba ngusihlalo we-AU, ukusebenzisana namalungu ombuso ngezindlela zokuthuthukisa ezezimali ezibandakanya wonke umuntu, izinhlelo zokuthenga ngokukhetha nokuhweba ngokukhetha kwabantu besifazane.
