1.12. Iviki lesihlanu Lezimbizo Zikazwelonke zikahulumeni elibanjwe kusukela mhla zi-7 zaze zaba yi-13 Lwezi 2016 ngaphansi kwesihloko esithi "Sisonke siqhubekisela iNingizimu Afrika phambili: Ikusasa lethu ‚Äì asilenze liphumelele" liveze ithuba lokuthi izakhamuzi zaseNingizimu Afrika zixoxisane nohulumeni ngendlela ebonakalayo. Leli thuba lokuxoxisana liphinda libe nesandla kubahlali abanolwazi futhi ababamba iqhaza, nokubalulekile ekufezeni Umbono we-2030 woHlelo Lokuthuthukiswa Kwezwe (i-NDP).
