Abantu bakwamanye amazwe ngeke bavunyelwe ukuthi babe nomhlaba okungowabo eNingizimu Afrika kodwa bazovunyelwa ukuthi benze isivumelwano sesikhathi eside sokuqasha umhlaba.
Ngokusebenzisa uHlelo Lwezinguquko Kwezomhlaba, umhlaba ongaphezu kwamahekthare ayizi-90 000 sewabelwe abalimi abancane, abahlali basemapulazini kanye nabasebenzi basemapulazini abayiziqashi.
