abayizinkulungwane ngezinkulungwane ababhalisile, ukuthi basebenzise ilungelo labo lokuvota oKhethweni Lukazwelonke noLwezifundazwe oluzayo, oluzobanjwa ngoLwesithathu, mhla ziyisi-8 kuNhlaba 2019, ukuze baveze uvo lwabo ngekusasa lezwe.
