Njengoba iNingizimu Afrika ingena eminyakeni elandelayo engama-25 ibuswa ngentando yeningi labantu, futhi ngenhloso yokufezekisa izinjongo ze-NDP, masizibekele injongo ebonisa isibindi neqholo, inhloso ezosibumbanisa sonke, esizozibophezela kuyona ngokuphelele futhi sifake kuyona wonke amandla nomfutho esinawo kanye nazo zonke izinsizaku-sebenza nezinsiza-sidingo zethu.
Njengoba singena kwiminyaka eyi-10 yokugcina yeNhloso-mbono yowezi-2030, masikubeke kucace bha ukuthi ngenjani iNingizimu Afrika esiyifunayo futhi sivumelane ngezinyathelo eziphathekayo futhi ezinohlonze esizozithatha ukufinyelela kuleyo Ningizimu Afrika esiyifunayo.
