Masizenze njengamanje lezi zibophezelo ‚Äì sizibhekise kithina uqobo futhi sizibhekise nakomunye nomunye wethu ‚Äì sibe sazi kahle kamhlophe ukuthi zizodinga izinsiza-sidingo kanye namandla ethu angeziwe, kodwa futhi ngokuqonda ukuthi uma siphumelela ukufezekisa lezi zinjongo, sizobe siphumelelile ukuletha uguquko olunohlonze ezweni lethu.
Ngaphezu kokudala amathuba omsebenzi kanye namanye amathuba ezomnotho, lokhu kusho ukuthi kumele siqinise uhlelo lwezibonelelo nemixhaso yomphakathi ehlinzekwa nguhulumeni futhi sinciphise nezindleko zokuphila.
Ukuzibophezela kwethu ekutheni kule minyaka eyi-10 ezayo asifuni ukubona noyedwa umuntu ebhuqabhuqwa yindlala eNingizimu Afrika, kuyisisekelo somzamo wethu wokuqeda ububha futhi sinciphise nokungalingani okukhona kuleli.
Kule minyaka emihlanu ezayo, sizokusheshisa ukuhlinzekwa kwabantu baseNingizimu Afrika abahlwempu ngezindlu ezakhiwe ezindaweni ezifanelekile futhi ezikulungele ukuhlaliswa kwabantu futhi sibahlinzeke nangomhlaba.
