Seziqalile ukukhiqiza imiphumela emihle futhi esemqoka izinyathelo esizithathile zokuqeda ukubanjwa ngobhongwane kombuso kanye nokulwisana nenkohlakalo, kubandakanya nezinyathelo zokuqinisa uPhiko Lukazwelonke Lwezokushushisa (i-NPA), uPhiko Lokuphenywa Kwamacala Akhethekile (i-SIU), uPhiko Lokuqoqwa Kwentela lwaseNingizimu Afrika (i-SARS) kanye neNhlangano Kahulumeni Yezokuvikela.
Kumele siqinisekise ukuthi iyabuyiswa imali kahulumeni entshontshiwe ukuze isetshenziselwe ukuhlinzeka izidingo-ngqangi kanye nengqalasizinda eyisisekelo edingeka kakhulu emiphakathini edla imbuya ngothi.
Sesinxuse uMqondisi Kazwelonke Wezokushushiswa Komphakathi (i-NDPP) ukuthi athuthukise uhlelo oluzophucula futhi luthuthukise kakhudlwana amandla okusebenza kanye nobunyoninco be-NPA, kubandakanya nokuqinisekisa ukuthi uqhutshwa kahle futhi ngobunono umsebenzi wokudliwa kwempahla etholakale ezenzweni zobugebengu nenkohlakalo.
INingizimu Afrika izoqhubeka nokudlala indima esemqoka kwezobudlelwane bamazwe omhlaba emizamweni yokuqinisekisa ukuthula nokuvikeleka emhlabeni, intuthuko egxile kubantu kanye nokuchuma nokuphumelela kwabantu bonke.
Sizosebenzisa isikhundla sethu njengelungu loMkhandlu Wezokuvikela we-UN, (i-UNSC), ukugqugquzela imizamo yokuxazulula izingxabano ngokuthula, ikakhulukazi kwizwekazi lase-Afrika
Kudingeka ukuthi sakhe ubambiswano oluqinile phakathi kukahulumeni, abasebenzi, imiphakathi kanye nezinhlangano zomphakathi.
Ukuze sikwazi ukufinyelela kuhlobo lweNingizimu Afrika esiyifisayo, sidinga isivumelwano sokusebenzisana nokubambisana esisha.
Uhulumeni kumele akhe isimo esifanelekile, azisebenzise ngobuhlakani izinsiza nezimali zakhe futhi atshale izimali ekuthuthukiseni abasebenzi baleli lizwe.
Izinhlangano zomphakathi wonkana kumele ziqhubeke nokudlala indima yazo yokuqinisekisa ukuthi uhulumeni uyaphendula ngemisebenzi yakhe, kodwa futhi kumele zihlanganyele nathi ekuthatheni izinyathelo eziphathekayo okuhloswe ngazo ukufezekisa izinjongo zethu sonke.
Lesi sivumelwano sokubambisana komphakathi wonkana sidinga ukuthi wonke umuntu afake isandla.
Sinethemba lokuthi amaqembu amelwe kuleli Phalamende azoba yingxenye esemqoka kulolu bambiswano, futhi alekelele, ahlinzeke ngemibono enohlonze nemiqondo ebonisa ubuhlakani obukhulu futhi aqhamuke nezixazululo kanye nemizamo ephathekayo ngenhloso yokuhlomulisa izwe lonkana.
Ukuze sikwazi ukuvuselela nokufaka ugqozi nofuqufuqu ekuqalisweni kwe-NDP, kumele siqinisekise ukuthi amehlo ethu ahlala ethe njo phambili lapho siphokophele khona.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika lapho wonke muntu ezophila kamnandi futhi ahlale ngokunethezeka, akhombe ngophakathi.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika ebeke eqhulwini izinhlelo zayo zokuthutha ngesitimela futhi okuyizinhlelo ezikhiziqa izitimela ezihamba ngesivinini esikhulu ezizoxhumanisa amadolobhakazi ethu nezindawo zasemakhaya ezisemajukujukwini ezwe lethu.
Kodwa-ke futhi sifuna iNingizimu Afrika lapho sizokwazi ukusebenzisa ngokuphelele amandla namakhono ethu ngenkathi siqhubeka endleleni ephokophele phambili.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika enomnotho ogxile kubuchwepheshe besimanjemanje lapho sisebenzisa khona izindlela-kusebenza zezempilo ezihlinzekwa ngohlelo-kusebenza lwe-inthanethi, nama-robotics kanye nokwelashwa okuhlinzekwa ezigulini ezikude kwezindawo zokwelapha, ngenkathi siqalisa ukusebenza kwe-NHI.
Kuyiphupho lami ukubona iNingizimu Afrika lapho kwakhiwa idolobha elisha sha esikhathini sombuso wentando yeningi labantu, elinamabhilidi amade, izikole, amanyuvesi, izibhedlela kanye namafemu.
Leli yiphupho okungaba ngelethu sonke futhi silifezekise ngempela.
Leli phupho lami ligqugquzelwe yingxoxo engibe nayo nabantu abanohlonze abanjengoDkt Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma, Dkt Naledi Pandor, Nkz Jessie Duarte kanye noMongameli wase-China u-Xi Jinping, owathi uma engixoxela ngokuthi i-China imatasa yakha idolobha elisha ebangeni elingamakhilomitha ayi-100 kusuka edolobheni lase-Beijing, wangenza ngibone ukuthi ngempela lingafezekiseka leli phupho lami.
Amadolobha anjengeGoli, i-Tshwane, iKapa kanye neTheku aseqala ukuphelelwa yindawo yokuhlalisa bonke abantu abafudukela ngobuningi emadolobheni.
Ngithanda ukumema abantu baseNingizimu Afrika ukuthi baqale ukubona ngamehlo ukwakhiwa kwedolobha elinjengaleli.
Thina siyisizwe saseNingizimu Afrika, esikwaziyo ukuthi ngoMthethosisekelo waso, sibuyise ithemba esimweni lapho belingasekho nelincane ithemba, esikwaziyo ukuhlinzeka ngamalungelo kubantu ababephucwe konke okungokwabo basala bengondinga sithebeni, futhi siyisizwe elikwaziyo ukuhlinzeka ngokunethezeka nokuvikeleka kubo bonke abantu balo, amadoda, abesifazane kanye nezingane.
Ungazibuza ukuthi ngingaba kanjani nethemba ezikhathini ezinzima njengalezi.
Siseyisona leso sizwe esishiwo ngenhla.
